      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can u go deeper into the part about dismantling the system? specifically, how would i argue that meritocracy is basically a myth or just a way to justify why some people are rich and others aren't? i want to show that the idea of 'working hard to get ahead' doesn't really apply when the playing field is this uneven.",
