      "content": "interesting. so if the meritocracy thing is basically a myth, how would you frame the counter-argument from people who say wealth redistribution is unfair or that it punishes success? i want to make sure i can address them in my essay, but i want the rebuttal to feel really powerful, like showing why their view is just based on ignoring the facts you just mentioned.",
